content:
I am currently working with Dr. Binh-Son Hua as a Research Resident at VinAI Research, the first AI research lab in Vietnam with a focus on fundamental research. My research focuses on solving practical problems using computer vision and deep learning. My current research interests include building efficient systems for 3D object detection and 3D data annotation. I am also interested in data-centric approaches in machine learning, and computational photography.
I am actively looking for a Ph.D. position starting in 2022.
